      <title>欧洲央行金多斯称宣布通胀胜利还为时过早</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/ecb-s-guindos-too-early-for-inflation-victory-despite-good-news</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行副行长路易斯·德金多斯表示，即使上个月通胀放缓幅度超过预期，欧洲央行仍不能说通胀已受到控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/ecb-s-guindos-too-early-for-inflation-victory-despite-good-news</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 09:50:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
